Subject: [PATCH 2/3] roc-pc-*rk3399: use PREBOOT for default usb start

The boards are using CONFIG_USB_KEYBOARD=y, but usb doesn't get setup
automatically on boot since CONFIG_USE_PREBOOT=y is not present.
---
